<Big> Map brought to you by Crackshot </big>

This is originally an FY map, but ive decided because of the size and game play that it would serve better as a gun game map, thus i am posting it in this section, the only changes to the map are that i have removed the buy zones so it would be a strictly gun game based map, ive had this publicly beta tested and got some great feedback. 

If you are interested in downloading the FY version then contact me and i will give you a link to it.



<big> IF YOU PLAN TO USE THIS ON YOUR SERVER PLEASE LET ME KNOW! </big>
